Class TransferProgressListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.transfer.TransferProgressListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.enterprisedt.net.ftp.EventListener

    public class TransferProgressListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.enterprisedt.net.ftp.EventListener
    Simple EDTFTPJ EventListener that only monitors file transfer progress. It forwards the information using a TransferProgressCallable object.
    Author:
    Thomas Debouverie
